docs.abstract: We’re interested in learning as much as possible about how employers manage their work forces.
docs.snippet: We’re interested in learning as much as possible about how employers manage their work forces.
docs.lead_paragraph: As Amazon is on the path to becoming the nation’s largest employer, we’ve been reporting on how it manages its vast work force. We’d like to deepen our knowledge of the employment model and practices at Amazon, as well as at other powerful companies.

headline.main: Do You Work at Amazon or Another Powerful Employer?
